nt commission of inquiry<br />\n3. Chief Executive, Secretary for Justice, Secretary for Security and Commissioner of Police to step down<br />\n4. Stop white terror and release all the protestors<br />\n<br />\nAgenda:<br />\n1. Strike on the 5 August (Monday)<br />\n2. Bring your own lunch to the public area in Taikoo Place on the 5 August<br />\n3. We will publish a Joint declaration on the 5 August. Details will be announced soon.<br />\n4. Dress code: Black<br />\n<br />\n*This event welcomes all individuals from the advertising industry to join. It doesn&rsquo;t represent any company, association or entity of any kind."},{"pid":"ea923532e82773c7f7304aaf2fa760656a4f860f","tid":1380947,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:37:40.000Z","msg":"廣告人push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205fb15764a49eb9e3837ff005fdf37b7e5af685","tid":1380947,"uid":151578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:37:51.000Z","msg":"不要說push / 推 試著說 8.5全港大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2b8eed5acd4290d586a705624f7e31aa25bb27","tid":1380947,"uid":151578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:39:16.000Z","msg":"不要說push / 推 試著說 8.5全港大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1223ffc3c9b8c7166b814d1fdd500ba506f25ac9","tid":1380947,"uid":151578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"不要說push / 推 試著說 8.5全港大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffaab6ce9e6c950fa804dd1734a15f1910bd072","tid":1380947,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color